text: læa klum chn khxng khea di ma ha khea phwk khea rib rxn mayang khea læa kxn hna nan phwk khea khey thakhwam chaw khea klaw wa “klum chn khxng chan xey! Hela ni khux luksaw khxng chan phwk nang nan brisuththi sahrab phwk than dangnan phwk than cng ya ke rng xallxh theid læa xya thahı chan khay hna tx khæk khxng chan ley mimi khn thi mi stisampchayya nı hmu phwk than bang hrux?”
